latestPosts.caption:
Back in 2022, I was in Mumbai at IHFF with team MuscleTech, sitting in the audience, watching the show i saw the bikini athletes compete, I remember feeling so inspired, i was completely in awe of how beautiful they looked , not just physically tbh, but in how they owned the stage. 
The energy, the presence, the way they carried themselves, I knew i wanted to be on that stage too and be myself and how fun it would be lol, i was so hyped i told @anaspathan__ that i am gonna be on that same stage one day And I’ll win. 
It felt like a crazy dream back then, but something in me believed it ngl i was all in! 
Fast forward to 2025 - 1 actually did it. I stepped on that same stage and won.
This journey wasn’t easy or quick but it was so much fun and I would do it all over again & i am gonna lol i just love this sport! 

A little about the early years, 
I’ve been into sports since I was in 7th standard, I played volleyball at the national level and represented All India University in both weightlifting and powerlifting. 
l’ve studied physical education through my bachelor’s and master’s, and started bodybuilding seriously in 2020, not seriously seriously because i didn’t have a coach and i did it almost by myself ( not a great idea btw ) 
I competed for the first time in 2021 in the bikini division in a local show and in Muscle Mania Delhi. 
But 2025 was the first time I prepped under a proper coach and shifted to the FitModel division. 
Super grateful for my coach @farhanbaig1996 🫡

Bodybuilding has taught me more than just how to train and eat. It’s changed me mentally, emotionally & helped me grow into someone l’m genuinely proud of. 
I’m sharing this clip as a reminder: whatever you want in life, it starts with belief. Even if it feels far away, even if no one else sees it , if you believe in it enough and are ready to put in the work, it can happen.
To anyone watching and dreaming: keep going.
One day, it’ll be you posting your “I did it “ reel 
Lovelove 🫶🏻

If you needed encouragement to get in the gym, HERE IT IS. 🦍
